{"tid":210033,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港失蹤人口","createTime":"2017-04-20T16:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T16:58:18.000Z","uid":94568,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1642fc7217b6c1088edf45965f0e1d8a9bcd2250","tid":210033,"uid":94568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:01:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/06_appeals_public/missing/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2F06_appeals_public%2Fmissing%2Findex.html&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5951965a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/06_appeals_public/missing/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n啱啱屎弗痕上黑警網睇下通緝犯名單，唔覺意㩒咗入去失縱人口到睇，發現原來有好多人係搵咗好多年都搵唔返。<br />\n睇返資料，原來香港每年有成4、5千個人失蹤，雖然尋回率都有成80-90%，但係每年都應該仲有百幾至幾百個人係仲失緊踨。<br />\n係個失蹤名單入面，見到啲啊婆啊伯失蹤個時都已經8、90歲，有啲仲起碼失蹤超過10年，好話唔好聽，佢哋應該唔餓死都老死咗，一年有咁多人失蹤，照理應該經常會係街或者行山嗰時發現到屍體，但係又無，咁究竟呢班人去咗邊呢？<br />\n<br />\n其實睇個失蹤名單時有少少心寒。"},{"pid":"3b5603702e0185188a4eeea9d1b252940cc11a50","tid":210033,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465150ab4b202b719b0cbafdc6c05db23c40ad73","tid":210033,"uid":94568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人都喺行山個時會驚撞到呢啲屍體？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3032585bb90dc6a5ad7a6e1eab8e6924dedcfeb","tid":210033,"uid":44193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有個故叫失蹤 就係講呢個題材"},{"pid":"808d5fb9b5372a0c5f7286243e6c3429198c3a11","tid":210033,"uid":92063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"08年有位加拿大籍女人去完重慶大慶就失左蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e974add884821c25fe08386ef7c2e4d5fa33308","tid":210033,"uid":94568,"like":0